      "title": "Power cut schedule until Friday announced",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka (PUCSL) has approved the power cut schedule from tomorrow (30) to Friday (September 2), PUCSL Chairman Janaka Rathnayake said.",
        "Accordingly, two hours and twenty minutes of power shedding will be imposed.",
        "The areas under the group A, B, C, D, E, F, G, H, I, J, K, L, P, Q, R, S, T, U, V and W will impose one-hour power cut during the daytime and one-hour and 20-minute power cut during the night."
      ],
